	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002356_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">Tuesday Evening </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Doctor </p>
<lb/><p>It will give 
<lb/>me great pleasure 
<lb/>to accept your 
<lb/>very kind - 
<lb/>invitation for 
<lb/>tomorrow 
<w>after-<lb break="no"/>noon.</w> We shall 
<lb/>take the liberty 
<lb/>to bring <persName>Anna 
<lb/>Mary who may</persName>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002356_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>play with your 
<lb/>little one till she 
<lb/>tired. Any hour 
<lb/>will suit us 
<lb/>so you may 
<lb/>tell <unclear cert="high"><persName>Tom</persName></unclear> which 
<lb/>will suit you 
<lb/>&amp; oblige Yours 
<lb/>Ever</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
			
